alttext: A jagged shape with an arched wave carved onto it.
description: A jagged shape which is uneven on all sides, as if all edges have been worn or broken away.  There seems to be a single line carved across the surface, a symmetrical wave which starts at the bottom left, arches up to the middle, and dips back down to the bottom right.  There does not seem to be any other decorations or markings.  The surface is mottled brown and patina green.

alttext: A long jagged shape.
description: An object which seems to have been part of a larger surface, but is now a horizontal jagged shape.  There are a few faint carved marks throughout the object, but it is hard to tell if they are decorative or symbolic of anything in particular.  The surface is a mottled brown with green patina, and there are spots of rust orange as well.

caption: Profile with rosette
alttext: A green helmet.
description: A round green helmet which is simple and without decoration.  It is seen from the side, so the shape is in profile.  It is mostly an even round shape, which flares out at the bottom.  There is a cutout for the face which consists of a series of arches and points outlining where the eye, cheek, and jaw of the wearer would be before curving around to meet with the bottom edge of the helmet. There is a border of parallel lines around the base towards the back of the helmet, but there is no other decoration.

alttext: An uneven half circle shape with rings.
description: A shape which seems to be a half circle, though damage to the bottom and right obscures the original shape, and the edges are now uneven.  There is a border of concentric lines around the top and left edges and the innermost line is partially visible along the uneven edges as well, indicating that the damage is mostly contained to the border edge. There is no other surface decoration that can be seen.  There are two rings at the top in the middle and right corner.  The surface is mottled brown, red, and green.

alttext: A half circle with damaged edges.
description: A half circle shape with a border of concentric lines.  There is damage along the edges, particularly at the top, corners, and right side. The surface is mottled dark grey and green.  There are a few lines, possible symbols, carved into the surface towards the top and slightly to the right.  They are only visible because they appear to be a slightly red color, having aged differently from the rest of the surface which is mostly a mottled brown and green.

alttext: A ridged helmet.
description: A helmet in a brown metal mostly covered in light green.  It has a rectangular cutout in the front for the face.  Running from the back to the front there are two parallel pointed ridges. There are also the barest indications of smaller parallel ridges on either side of those two central ones. There is a simple line border around the face cutout, aside from that there is no other surface decoration.

alttext: A crying woman visible from the waist up with her hands together.
description: A light-skinned woman gazes down and to the left, her hands pressed together as if in prayer. She wears a white veil and a dark blue, subtly shiny cloak with metallic golden trim. Three tears flow from each eye, trailing down her cheeks. Her brow is furrowed, and there are circles under her eyes. The woman’s hair is curly and luminous, her tears are perfectly clear, and the folds of her clothing and sheerness of her veil are very detailed. The background behind the woman is gold and covered with small brown dots.

alttext: Five figures interact with each other.
description: The vessel is black with a wide spout and two handles that connect the body of the vessel to the rim.  In red, five figures in draping clothing face each other.  The farthest left figure holds dishes, a figure next to them who seems bald holds a staff, and the other two of the central figures shake hands, one holds a trident and the other appears to have a weapon sheathed at their hip.  There are floral motifs along the upper rim of the vessel and geometric patterns border the scene.

alttext: Red-brown, intact, terracotta bowl that is shallow and wide, shown on a light gray background
description: This red-brown terracotta bowl is about three times as wide as it is tall. The bowl has no visible breaks or cracks, but there are several tiny chips on the otherwise smooth surface. The short base of the bowl is wide and flat and is about half the width of the top. From the bottom, the sides of the bowl curve outward, perpendicular to the base, then curve upward and widen as they reach the rim, which is flat and bends slightly outward. There are two narrow incised lines that circle the interior rim. There is a light gray background.

alttext: A marble sculpture depicts the head of a man with a long beard and rows of curls above the forehead.
description: A white marble sculpture depicts the head of a man with a long rectangular beard. The beard consists of four rows of long curved tufts of hair, rendered in a stylized geometric pattern. There is a thick ring of three rows of stacked corkscrew curls above the forehead. In contrast to the more stylized hair patterns, the facial features are more classically rendered as smooth and realistic. The eyes are almond-shaped, and the nose is thin and straight. There is some minor chipping at the brow at right.

alttext: Bronze plaque of Christ carrying the cross, surrounded by several other figures.
description: Shiny, rectangular bronze plaque with three-dimensional image of Jesus Christ, a halo on his head, carrying a cross on his left shoulder. Behind him is a figure with a battle helmet holds a rope looped around Jesus’s chest. Before him is a female figure with a halo holding a strip of fabric with a man’s face on it. Over Jesus’s left shoulder is a crowd of people, most with helmets and spears. In front of the crowd is a child figure holding a cylindrical object in their left hand.

alttext: A dark bronze sculpture of a man sitting cross-legged on a pedestal.
description: The bronze sculpture is of a man sitting on a pedestal facing the viewer. The bronze is dark in color with hints of red. The bottom of the pedestal is detailed with large petals. The man is wearing a robe that drapes over his whole body. His legs are crossed and his feet are on top of the opposite knees. The man’s right arm is down by his side with his palm pointing down and facing the viewer. His left arm is bent up and there is a small round object held in his left hand. His earlobes are long and his hair is put up in a small bun on top of his head.

alttext: A fishing boat docked in a harbor with a landscape in the background
description: At center, a sailboat with its sails taken down floats in a harbor, its stern tied by several thin ropes to a dock. The water is calm, reflecting the bright blue sky above. A smaller boat with its sails up floats in the corner where the dock meets a sea wall. The tan wall and the rolling hills in the distance beyond it, are loosely sketched in large blocks of color,  the buildings of a small city indicated only by white and brown swatches. No people are present, either aboard the boat or on land.

alttext: Painting of man in black robe with blue background and inscription
description: Portrait of a light-skinned man facing toward the viewer’s right. He has ear-length, curly gray hair, a furrowed brow, wrinkles, brown eyes, a large nose, and a round, dimpled chin. He wears a black robe with a red and white collar. The middle of the collar has a tied black cord. Behind the man is a solid blue background. At the top of the painting is the inscription “D. MARTINUS LUTHERUS.” with another line of smaller, less legible text beneath. To the left of the man is another inscription in small print reading “1546” just above a small curly shape.

caption: Chapter 20: A is painting on left, B is calligraphy on right
artist seal, detail of right scroll
detail of artist's inscription, signature and seals

alttext: A drawing of a woman standing for a portrait in a long dress.
description: The drawing in graphite on white paper depicts a woman standing center-page facing left in three quarters, her gaze directed to the viewer. She wears a long dress ornamented in striped patterns on the sleeves and prominent frills down the bust. Her hands are linked at her waist, and a folded garment is draped over her left arm. Her dark, straight hair is parted at center and just visible beneath a frilled kerchief or bonnet.

caption: front
alttext: A wooden sculpture of a slender person standing upright on a detailed pedestal. They are wearing draped cloth that covers their legs and goes across their shoulder and chest. They are wearing a small headpiece and have short hair.
description: The wooden sculpture is of a slender person standing upright on a pedestal. The pedestal is wide at the bottom, has a small midsection, and is wide at the top with organic carved details on it. The sculpture is light brown and medium brown in color. The person is wearing draped cloth that covers their legs, torso, and goes over their left shoulder. Their left hand is bent up so their closed hand is close to their chest. Their right hand is down at their side with their hand open and pointing down. They have short hair and are wearing a headpiece. They have a dot in between their eyebrows.

alttext: White ceramic full length sculpture of two women standing side by side
description: Two young women are sculpted leaning against each other in a relaxed pose. They each have long wavy hair and wear long flowing robes. One woman, slightly taller, looks off to her right and stands with one leg crossed in front of the other, gathering part of her robe to her side in her right hand, as she rests her left arm around the neck of the other woman. The second woman looks down and to her left, reaching up with one hand to touch the hand of the first woman, as she also holds the first woman around her waist.

alttext: A bronze sculpture of a male figure holding a shell.
description: The sculpture shows a nude male figure kneeling on a square base. The torso is twisted slightly to the right, the head is bent down to the shell being held against the chest by the right arm. The shell is supported by the left arm which bent and crosses the chest with the hand cupped against the upper right arm. The surface of the figure is green with patches of dark brown.

alttext: Spherical, dark metal censer with openwork lid and chains.
description: Spherical censer (ceremonial incense holder) in dark metal. The censer has two halves, the bottom being solid and the top having an elaborate openwork structure. The shapes of the carved top are mostly botanical, resembling leaves, vines, and hearts. They are arranged in nearly, but not perfectly, symmetrical sections. The censer has a tab with a hole in it on the top. At four points around the middle of the censer are raised holes through which long, thin chains are threaded. The four chains are attached to an X-shaped metal piece.

caption: vol. 2, table of contents p. 2 rear and p. 1 front
front
alttext: A flat jade pendant of a woman that is rectangular in shape and has been carved with fine lines to outline a wrapped robe, belt, a swirling shape by her feet, her face, and her hair which goes behind her head.
description: A flat jade pendant of a woman that is rectangular in shape and yellow and orange in color. It is shown laying flat vertically on a black background. Ithas been carved with fine lines to outline a wrapped robe, belt, a swirling shape by her feet, her face, and her hair which goes behind her head. Her sleeves come together in front of her stomach. She has a downturned mouth, round nose, small eyes, and a squared hairline.

alttext: A wooden sculpture of a partially divided ovoid form with a blunt, rounded end on a flat wooden base.
description: The sculpture made from a single block of wood and shows a smaller ovoid shape with a blunted edge set on an angle and has a small raised disc near the top edge. The center of the sculpture has been carved out but is joined at one end by a sloping indentation. The larger shape balloons out slightly at the base and is squared off at the top. The grain of the wood is visible, each section has small cracks on the top edges.

alttext: A drawing of columns in light gray with flared segmented bases.
description: The drawing is of columns which are thicker in width at the front of the drawing and get thinner as they recede and fill the upper half of the picture space. The columns rise out of flared, segmented cones, the segments are defined by black lines. In the lower right corner, resting on one of the segments is a small egg shape which casts a shadow. The drawing is in shades of gray.

alttext: A curved pale teal and purple bowl.
description: A curved pale teal and purple colored bowl shown on a white background from the side. It has curved walls and a small, bare foot. The lip is faded from thinned glaze.

alttext: A black-and-white photograph portrays a group of men lining up in front of an office service counter.
description: A black-and-white photograph shows an overhead shot of a group of nine men lining up along the center from the lower right to the upper left in front of a service counter on a large square tile floor, along with a few men waiting in a separate line at the bottom of the frame. Most of the men wear suits and fedora hats. The third white man from the left looks up at the viewer.

alttext: A black-and-white photograph portrays a man with hands on hips facing a bank’s storefront window.
description: A black-and-white photograph shows the upper half of a man, off center to the left, wearing a pleated beanie, a long-sleeve shirt, and overalls with crisscross straps, his back to the viewer with hands on hips, looking at a poster in a bank’s storefront window. There is a large clock in the center of the window, another poster hanging on the right, and the name of the bank runs from the center to the upper right. Reflected in the window are the cars and shops on the opposite side of the street, and the profile of another man holding a camera at left.

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped gold coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: On the side of the coin on the left is the bust of a man facing left, with a long straight beard, short cropped hair, wearing a pearl headband, clothing draped over shoulder; surrounding the border, the Latin characters: F L C L / I V L I A / N V S / P F / A V G. The other side of the coin depicts a bearded man standing facing left, wearing flowing robes, a crown, holding an ornate staff in left hand, a small cloth in his right; surrounding the border, the Latin characters: V I R T V S / E X E R C I / T V S / R O M A N O R V M / A N T / B.

caption: Illustration of the possible position when cast, by F. G. Bewer

alttext: A porcelain disc shaped container with two small holes in the top
description: In the shape of a puck with one flattened edge, this small container has been molded with a raised texture that depicts a fish with its head curled under itself, almost touching its tail. The surface has been painted a rich blue, and where the raised ridges of the scales and other details are, the white porcelain underneath shows through to highlight those lines. On the top surface there are two small holes, one in the center and one on the outer edge just behind the fish’s head.

alttext: Bronze figure of man on pedestal with candle holder in right hand
description: Shiny, dark bronze figurine of a man. He has a long mustache, a textured hat, and chin-length hair. His body is covered in carved wavy lines, indicating hair. A loincloth is wrapped around his hips. His left elbow is bent with his hand in a fist. In his raised right hand is a base for a candle. It appears to be eight-sided, and it is larger at the top than the bottom. The bottom of the base has a circular cutout. Extending down from the man’s feet are two small structures connected to a large circular base with carved ridges.

caption: Chapter 41: A is painting on left, B is calligraphy on right

alttext: A silver colored, open tin can with a brown painted cross on the front next to a  flat-tip screwdriver with a brown handle.
description: The artwork contains two objects, an open tin can containing lubricant and a screw driver. The tin can is silver and has a brown cross, in the orientation of an addition sign, hand painted on the front. The tin is open and shows the yellowed lubricant inside. The screw driver has a brown handle and a flat-tip.

alttext: Weathered, pale blue translucent glass beaker with straight sides that narrow inward slightly to a rounded rim
description: The exterior of this translucent pale blue glass beaker is heavily weathered. It does not have a smooth surface, but instead shows many pits and etched marks and has patches of light-colored dirt accretions near the base. The beaker is slightly wider than it is tall. It has a squat, rounded shape that tapers slightly inward at the top. The rim is rounded and has a rolled smooth lip that does not show weathering. The color of the lip appears to be a slightly darker shade of blue.

caption: detail of head on handle in profile
Chapter 5: A is painting on left, B is calligraphy on right

alttext: A black and white photograph of people working in large room mounted on board with white lettering.
description: The black and white photograph shows a row of people sitting facing a brick wall with large, closed windows. The ceiling is beamed. There is a vertical rack with rows of tobacco leaves on the right side. In front of the rack are several crates and several barrels. The caption reads: Tobacco drying in the work room poisons the air.

alttext: A two-piece suit in thick gray felt.
description: The two-piece suit is made of a thick, slightly fuzzy gray felt. The jacket has a collar and narrow notched lapels edged in black. The jacket is unlined, it has a breast pocket and two pockets with flaps at waist height. It has no buttons. The trousers are straight legged with sharp creases down the front.

alttext: A black and white photograph showing an arm and a piece of equipment.
description: The black and white photographs shows an arm in a white shirt from the left side, the hand is holding a small round piece of equipment on a board with a diagram and writing in white which reads in part, kopf, isolator. The board is sitting on a table with a pail, three white containers and a sheaf of paper at the top of the photograph.

alttext: A nude woman seated, raising her arm and wiping herself with a towel
description: Heavy black chalk lines on yellowed paper show a nude woman seen from behind and turned toward the left. She is seated and leaning forward, her left arm raised with her hand bent back facing the viewer. Her head bows forward and her hair is tied up in a bun, as she reaches her right arm around to her left side, drying herself with a towel that she holds at her side. Dark shading on her right side contrasts with strong light on her left side.

caption: Figure on right is BR59.32, figure on left is BR59.33.
detail of side A, 3/4 from left

alttext: Standing nude woman holding upside-down parasol
description: The image for this drawing is black-and-white. A woman stands facing away from the viewer and slightly toward the right. Her hair is up in a bun, her face looks downward, and her shoulders are a bit slouched. Her right arm is bent, her elbow resting against her hip. In her arm she holds the handle of an upside-down parasol. The parasol is significantly less detailed than the woman. Its handle is a simple dark line, and its top part is a wide oval. Whistler’s “butterfly” signature is written on the right side of the parasol.

caption: recto
alttext: A drawing of two women shaking hands beneath a pediment.
description: The drawing in graphite on tracing paper depicts a circular icon of two women shaking hands beneath a pediment and blue sky. On the left is a woman standing in profile facing the right of the page. She wears a long, sleeveless draped garment and a crown. In her left hand she grasps a tall staff, and her right hand grasps the left hand of the woman on page right. The woman on page right stands in three quarters facing the left of the page. She wears a long draped garment with a hooded shawl over her head, and holds a tall ornamental cross in her left hand against her shoulder. Behind the women is a decorated pediment and frieze, under which is an ornate altar with an infant motif. To either side of the pediment are flame-topped columns.

alttext: A standing figure points to a starry sky and addresses five seated figures
description: At left, a muscular figure stands, gesturing with an outstretched right arm while pointing upward at a star filled sky with his left. He is shown in profile, facing a group of seated figures at center and right. Each of these figures are older, bearded, and wear long robes. The figure nearest the speaker buries his head in his knees and folds his hands in front of him. The others are grouped close by, listening and seated on the ground, with a stone archway behind them. The image is surrounded by a border decorated with text and a motif of small figures floating upward from a large sleeping bearded figure who occupies the lower margin.

caption: The Cowgirls Attend Krishna, verso, text

alttext: Line drawing of the head and shoulders of a woman in profile
description: Thin, faintly sketched lines with some darker accents depict the profile of a woman facing right and tilting her head back. She wears a gown with a low cut neck and ruffled shoulders, and wears her hair pulled back in a bun. Shading on the bridge of her nose indicates light shining on her from below. She squints and smiles slightly, wearing dark makeup on her lips and eyes. At upper right, a quickly drawn poster on a wall shows a man in a tailcoat and top hat, facing away from us and holding a conductor’s baton.

caption: sections E, F, G and H
overall
alttext: Pentagonal, gold wooden panel with painted image of man on cross surrounded by crowd
description: In the center of the panel is a light-skinned man hanging on a cross with cherubs in blue robes at either side. A gold halo crowns the man’s head. Below the man is a crowd of many seated, standing, and kneeling light-skinned figures in colorful garments. Five figures at the bottom left wear golden halos, and one of them, wearing a blue robe, lies in the lap of another. Several figures are in military helmets and armor. One such figure sits atop a brown horse with its head bowed. Above the crowd are red flags with gold script.

alttext: Pastel drawing of reclining nude woman on brown paper
description: A light-skinned woman lies on her left side, facing the viewer. Her left arm is bent, her hand under her cheek, and her right arm is draped over her head. Her ankles are crossed, and her legs bend toward the background, with the tips of her feet cut off by the margin of the paper. The woman is pale and slender with dark hair and pink cheeks. Above her is a sheer expanse of red-orange pastel; below her is an expanse of gold pastel. Whistler’s “butterfly” signature appears in dark pastel in the upper left corner.

caption: detail of marks and initials under base

alttext: Black and white image of opaque rounded amphora with two handles, short neck, wide flat lip, and etched pattern decorations
description: This black and white image shows an opaque, rounded amphora. The spherical body rests on a short base and has a slimmer, short neck that turns into a flat, wide lip. There is a white patch, perhaps a chip, on the left side of the base. There are two symmetrical ribbon handles that rest of the shoulder and attach at the top under the lip. The upper half of the body is decorated with curling, etched lines that resemble tendrils of a plant. The lower half is etched with a horizontal rope pattern and an arched, brick-like design.

alttext: Black-and-white engraving of woman and child sitting above winged figures
description: A smiling woman sits on a large, billowy cloud suspended in the air. She wears a long veil that drapes down to her feet. She holds a nude child in front of her. Below them are three figures with large wings. The figure in the middle stands over another figure on the ground with ram’s horns, batlike wings, and a long reptilian tail. The figure on the right holds a kneeling, frowning child by the shoulders. In the background is a mountain range and a sea with sailboats.

caption: recto
alttext: Study of a man in a coat standing
description: On a tall thin rectangular off white sheet, light graphite lines depict a male standing figure, filling most of the narrow space. The young man stands facing the viewer, looking downward, tucking his chin into the collar of his coat and hunching his shoulders up. He holds his right forearm in front of his chest and tucks his hand into his buttoned coat. His left hand is jammed deep into his pocket at his side. Light shading indicates the folds of his clothing.

alttext: Page featuring several sketches of nude woman
description: The image for this artwork is black-and-white. On a single sheet of paper, we see sketches of various views of a nude woman. She is slender, with her hair tied up. In the central, most detailed sketch, the woman stands facing the viewer, bending at the hip to touch her knees. In the top right she stands on tiptoe with her hands above her head, facing away from the viewer. At bottom right she looks back over her shoulder and crosses her arms over her chest. Other sketches show just her head or isolated lines representing curves of her body.

caption: Detail of the mineralized metal at the break
Detail of the interior of the strainer component
drawing of inscription on the helmet band

alttext: Detailed oil paint portrait depicts a seated woman clothed in a black dress, pearl jewelry, and white gloves.
description: A light-skinned woman with brown eyes and dark hair gazes slightly to her right with a neutral expression. She is seated against a dark background. Visible from the waist up, she wears a black dress with a lace collar and short sleeves. Around her neck are two strings of pearls, and she wears looped pearl earrings. Wearing a double strand of pearls atop her head, her hair is parted down the middle and pulled back. Her hands rest in her lap, displaying pearl bracelets on her bare right forearm. Fabric is draped over her left arm, with her left gloved hand visible, holding the right glove.

alttext: A black and white photograph of a view of a cemetery.
description: The black and white photograph shows a view of a cemetery. The tombstones and raised tombs in the front are crisscrossed by diamond shaped black shadows. The upper half of the photograph shows tombstones with crosses on top, a small peak roofed structure with an arched window and a cross at the peak. Behind and in shadow are leafless tree branches and more tombstones.

alttext: A black and white photograph of three men in front of a building.
description: The photograph shows three men standing in front of a building. On the left a medium dark skinned man wearing a white shirt with sleeves rolled up to the elbow and a white apron is seen in profile facing right. In the center a medium light skinned man with a small moustache, wearing a hat, a white shirt, black tie and gray suit a folded newspaper tucked under his left arm, faces the viewer. On the right a Black man wearing a hat, a white shirt with sleeves rolled up to the elbow and dark trousers, leans against a pilaster with a scroll decoration

alttext: Botanical watercolor drawing of a stem and leaf of the Amaranthus plant.
description: A delicate stem of six salmon-pink slender panicles of tiny flowers rest under one large heart-shaped medium green leaf with well-defined veins that emanate from the center to the outer edge of the leaf. The panicles are fanned out and reach up as the stem forks into two divisions, the leaf points downward toward the left. The stem is slender and light green in color. Slight shadows underneath both give depth and dimensionality to the drawing; the background is antique white. Manuscript of the Latin name in the lower right.

alttext: A woman and man seated beneath a tree surrounded by their family and a flock of sheep
description: At center, wearing long robes and holding open books in their laps, a woman and a man  sit facing the viewer. Beneath a large tree they are surrounded their family. At left and right, seven sons holding shepherd’s crooks kneel, while three daughters kneel in front of them at center. In the foreground, a line of sheep lie sleeping. Behind the family a large flock of sheep grazes. In the distance at left a large stone church is seen while at right there is a row of barns. In the margin above the image in a cloud motif are the hand-lettered words to the first line of a prayer. Below is text from the biblical Book of Job, between a cow and sheep.

alttext: A black and white photograph of a white building with windows and two metal platforms.
description: The black and white photograph shows a portion of a white building. There are two rows of eight windows. The top row of windows have triangular decorations above that are part of the building. The top row of windows are damaged, the first from the left has a broken pane, the second has a door inserted in the frame, the third is boarded up and the bottom of the fourth is boarded up. The lower row windows are also damaged, the first and second from the left have broken panes, the third and fourth are partially boarded up. The metal platforms are attached beneath the third and fourth windows on the right.

alttext: A black and white photograph of a figure carved in stone.
description: The black and white photograph shows a simplified face, carved into the center of a flat stone surface. The face has round eyes, an inverted Y-shape runs down from between the eyes to just above the round nose with two roughly shaped holes. A long gash in the stone runs from below the nose to outside the carved-out area. Above the face are roughly broken lines radiating out and up to the top the image. The flat surface of the stone is heavily scored with fine crisscrossed lines.

alttext: A small bound volume of forty-six lithographs.
description: The small bound volume contains forty-six lithographs. The cover is in a swirling design of brown, gold and cream. The title page shows a piece of equipment consisting of tubes connected with smaller tubes. The number six is at the bottom of the page. The title printed across the top is peccus complexus circumventus (asfucus). The book is tied with a lavender ribbon.

alttext: A black and white photograph of a building with an entry porch and several windows.
description: The black and white photograph shows a portion of a light colored building with a dark entry porch over a door and two smaller windows. There is a light behind the window on the right which shows a design of small square and a diamond shape in the center. There are two larger windows on either side. There is a large window centered over the porch on the floor above. It has a large center window flanked by two narrower windows. There are windows on either side of the center arrangement of windows. There are dark decorative panels above the windows, a square that rises to a center peak.

caption: Drawing by Catherine S. Alexander, February 2003, and amended August, 2007.
painting proper
alttext: A painted scroll with dark paper with many repeating seated figures. All of the figures are outlined in white and in a cross-legged position. At the center is a larger figure encircled by smaller figures in a square outline. The square is surrounded by more figures in rows.
description: The painted scroll is a short rectangle shape and has a black background. The scroll is framed by a black and white floral pattern. The scroll is covered with many figures that are outlined in white and sitting cross-legged and have circles around their bodies. At the center of the scroll is a larger figure encircled by smaller figures. There is a square outline around them. The square is surrounded by more small figures in rows. There are two larger figures at the bottom corners of the scroll. The figures repeat to the end of the page.

alttext: Three young women sit around an elderly bearded man
description: At center, a white haired man with a flowing beard sits in a long robe, facing the viewer and gesturing with each arm extended outward. Three young women in robes sit around him, one leaning in against him at either side, and a third seen from behind, kneeling and facing him. Pairs of sheep recline on the floor in the foreground at lower left and lower right. Behind on the wall are three quickly sketched pictures on the wall at center, left, and right.

alttext: A black and white photograph of people in an open space.
description: The black and white photograph shows a large open space in an urban setting. The open area is paved with a high wall bordering the back from the left. There is an opening on the right side where a view of buildings on the street is visible. In the foreground on left is a young man wearing dark clothing, a white shirt and a tie. There is a person wearing plus-fours, their back to the view, immediately behind. A Black man in the center is pushing a full wheelbarrow. A group of people is entering the area from the opening on the right.

alttext: Still life on a musical theme with an instrument, sheet music, books, and other objects on a small wooden table.
description: The dark wooden table is set in front of dark grey drapery on the left. Two old stained sheets of music hang down off the edge of the table in the center. Three small books have fallen over from the left into the center, an unlit candle in a pewter holder pointing right sits askew on the edge of the smallest book. A clarinet rests diagonally on top of the books, its mouthpiece on the table, crisscrossing behind the candlestick. A small bronze bust sits in the back of the scene. Light falls from above onto the table objects.

alttext: A black and white photograph of fragments of posters.
description: The black and white photograph shows an area of a wall where multiple posters have been pasted. Only fragments of the posters remain and are unevenly torn leaving only individual letters or parts of words visible. A black shape obscures a section of the right side and a wide line of black extends slightly to the left and down to the bottom edge.

caption: detail: coat of arms on largest beaker

alttext: Christ in the center holds a large wooden cross over his left shoulder, a crowd surrounds him.
description: A man in the lower right, crouched position, grabs the robe on Christ’s chest, there’s a hammer in his belt. Two praying women are at Christ’s back, a third is on his right kneeling and holding up a white cloth. His right hand is raised in a benediction gesture, his troubled face looks up to the left. His robes are red and purple, thorns wrapped around his head. An armed solider behind the cross turns back yelling at the crowd with an angry face, there are more soldiers with weapons behind him.

caption: recto
alttext: Six head studies of young women and men are portrayed in various angles and profiles in a semi-circle around.
description: Clockwise from lower left a slightly portly woman looks up to the left. Top left the same woman with chin up looks right. Top right a man’s face looks slightly down. Middle right a lady’s head turns right in profile, we see side of her neck and cap unturned in the back. In lower right a man looks down and slightly left, his forehead and black hair are prominent. In the middle the lady wearing a cap looks to the right, her face drawn in three-quarter view. The faces have delicate and accurate details while hair, neck, have less detail

caption: detail of artist signature and seals at upper right

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped gold coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: On the side of the coin on the left is a series of concentric circles with Arabic calligraphy within the borders of each circle. The other side of the coin also depicts a series of concentric circles with Arabic calligraphy within the borders of each circle.

caption: Detail of crest with spot of cuprite
High dynamic range composite x-ray, side view

alttext: A black and white photograph of a man cutting a stalk of sugar cane.
description: The black and white photograph shows a bearded man in light colored clothing wearing a hat with a brim. His right arm is raised, he holds a machete in his right hand. His left arm is outstretched, and his gloved hand holds a stalk of sugar cane. The man is slightly twisted at the waist. There are stalks of sugar cane on the left side of the photograph and leaves are visible in the bottom foreground.

alttext: A curved light blue bowl.
description: A light blue colored bowl that is shown standing on a white background from the side. It has no foot and curved walls.

caption: detail of seals in lower left corner
detail of monk figure at right (after conservation treatment and remounting)
open inkstone box (left); interior of lid (right)
detail of inscription, signature, and seals
detail of artist's signature and seal

alttext: Painting of head and torso of young woman
description: A light-skinned young woman can be seen from the waist up. She faces the viewer. Her red hair is tied up, and she has curly bangs. Her eyes appear to be blue or green, and her mouth and cheeks are a coral pink. She wears an olive-colored dress with a large gray ruff-like collar. The background behind her is a dark blue-gray. The woman is painted in a soft, almost blurred style. The paint shows some signs of age, including some cracking all over and some flaking near the edges of the image.

alttext: Watercolor of a large tan field with people and buildings in the background
description: The foreground of this image is a large yellow-tan field, with shading suggesting hills and grass. A few small groups of people are scattered in on the right side of the field and on its back perimeter. One figure on the right has a round red shape suggesting a parasol. On a background of low, broad hills, we can see roofs of buildings, including the black steeple of what is presumably a church in the middle. The figures and landscape in this work are not presented descriptively; their features are suggested by shape and color but not rendered in detail.

alttext: A group of figures stands on a stone platform above a crowd surrounded by a stone wall.
description: On a stone platform, several light-skinned adults and children stand looking down into a crowd. They all wear brightly colored robes. Three men in the back wear helmets and hold spears. The children hold golden platters. In the crowd below, many light-skinned people are dancing, playing instruments, and reaching their arms up toward the platform. A couple reclines in the foreground with a dog. In the anterior wall, there is a large doorway bordered by columns. Through the doorway is a softly lit landscape with mountains and trees. This painting is oval-shaped and sits in an ornate golden rectangular frame.

alttext: A pastel drawing depicting a landscape with a solitary figure.
description: A pastel drawing showing a landscape with a golden field and a path extending through it from left to right. In the center of the field is a single tree topped with orange foliage. To the left of the tree a person bends from the waist down towards the ground. In the background, the field is surrounded by greenery through which two houses can be seen.

alttext: A painting of lacquered tree bark applied to red painted canvas with white highlights and black burn marks.
description: The painting is made of lacquered bark applied to canvas which has been painted red. The red paint shows through cracks in the wood. A larger area at the top center is white with black burn marks, the white extends down a small crack. Small round burn marks appear unevenly placed up the left side and across the top, larger burned areas, some highlighted by red appear across the bottom and in the center. An uneven band of red paint extends from the top to the bottom of the right side.

alttext: Painting of head and torso of young figure
description: A figure faces the viewer, looking slightly upward and to the left. They appear young and androgynous, with shoulder-length brown hair, thick eyebrows, large brown eyes, pink cheeks, red lips, and a prominent chin. The figure wears a purple garment. Because of the painting style and some possible pigment discoloration, it is difficult to see the details of the figure’s clothing. They also wear a small black hat with a large red feather attached diagonally across the front. The background behind them is dark green.

caption: top
alttext: Long oval-shaped box with scenes of women and animals
description: This long, narrow box has rounded edges. On the top side of the box are three oval-shaped images, each surrounded by a gold painted “frame.” The large one in the center depicts a light-skinned woman in a pink dress gazing upward. The smaller images show brown eagles with hooked beaks. The sides of the box have similar decoration. Each has a small central medallion with a portrait of a light-skinned woman. Larger images on either side show deer walking and reclining. The entire box is glossy with a yellow tinge. One end of the box has a cutaway portion, creating a cap.

alttext: A painted scroll depicting a large, brown panel of a man in a white robe sitting beneath a drooped tree branch. A white panel at the top shows Chinese writing in black ink. The two panels are connected by a blue and white patterned background.
description: The painted scroll shows two panels of paper that are bordered by a blue and white patterned background. The bottom panel is large and brown and depicts a man in the center sitting facing the viewer and dressed in a white robe. His robe is loose and drapes off of his right shoulder. His right leg is down and bent inward while his left leg is bent up. His right arm is straight down and his left hand rests on his left knee. He has a long, black beard and is wearing a dark hat. Above him are drooped branches with many green leaves and there are tree trunks to the left of the image. The second panel is above the brown panel and is white. It is just as wide as the brown panel but a quarter of the height. This panel has vertical rows of Chinese writing all over it in black ink. There is a small red symbol to the bottom-left of the panel.

caption: profile
alttext: A pale blue, low bowl with vertical lines widely spaced out on the side. The flat, thin top rim protrudes out. The rim curves to mimic large petals. The inside is aqua colored. The four feet on the bottom curl out like leaves.
description: A pale blue, low bowl stands on a grey background and is shown at its side. On the sides are vertical lines widely spaced out. The flat, thin top rim protrudes out and curves to mimic large petals. The inside is aqua colored. There are tan lines along the edges of the rim from thinned glaze. The four, stout feet on the bottom curl out like leaves and are also glazed magenta.

caption: top
alttext: A circular dish shown from above. It is pale blue with an off-white rim.
description: A circular dish shown from above on a grey background. It is pale blue-green with a thin, off-white rim.

caption: profile
alttext: An aqua and magenta ceramic flower pot with vertical lines widely spaced out on the side. The flat, thin top rim protrudes out. The rim curves to mimic large petals. The inside is blue.
description: An aqua and magenta ceramic flower pot stands on a grey background and is shown from its side. The aqua glaze mixes with the magenta glaze throughout the piece and the inside is also blue. On the sides are vertical lines widely spaced out. Tan lines are along the edges and indents from thinned glaze. The flat, thin top rim protrudes out. The rim curves to mimic large petals. The piece has a small foot.

alttext: A watercolor of a prancing white horse with a man running on its far side under a blue sky.
description: A watercolor of a white horse with wild eyes and a flowing tail prancing to the right through an empty landscape. On the far side of the horse a man wearing a turban, red pantaloons and turquoise leggings runs closely by. In the distance a dark hill slopes down from the left of the drawing under a bright blue sky.

caption: Maquette for Gift of the Bridge
Maquette for Long Leavers Gate (In Steps)
When Winter on Forgotten Woods Moves Somber...

alttext: One side of a striped canvas beach cabana in profile
description: At center a cabana stands in bright sunlight, its striped canvas side lashed to poles staked in the sandy ground. Seen from one side, its dark and light stripes are interrupted in places by similarly striped square patches at random intervals.  At top right, the edge of an awning can be seen, jutting off from the top from another side. Just beyond, at middle right its short shadow stretches back. At left in the middle distance, a bicycle is parked in front of a small building, and foliage fills the background in the upper third.

alttext: Clusters of leaves on thin branches silhouetted against a bright sky
description: Slender branches reach down into view from top left to top middle-right in the foreground. The end of each branch produces eight or so small stems which each hold individual, rounded, heart shaped leaves that show black against a bright sky behind it. One of the longest branches reaches down to the lower right, but most are clustered in the top third of the piece. In the lower left and lower right corners, tall trees with foliage can be seen in the distance, and a narrow black line borders the piece.

alttext: A black and white, and color, super 8mm film on video with sound.
description: The video shows the artists exploring and documenting the underground spaces of New York City. The artist chose a range of sites (New York Central railroad tracks, Grand Central Station, 13th Street, Croton Aqueduct in Highgate, etc.) to show the variety and complexity of the underground spaces and tunnels in the metropolitan area.

alttext: A jade pendant that is a long and narrow rectangle in shape and pale yellow in color with some red discoloration. There are small, curved lines throughout the piece that create swirling shapes.
description: The jade pendant is a long and narrow rectangle shape and shown vertically on a dark grey background. The pendant is pale yellow in color with some red discoloration. There are small, curved lines on the piece that create a regular swirling pattern throughout. The edges of the pendant are straight and flat.

caption: front
alttext: A jade sculpture of a turtle from a bird’s eye view. The turtle’s shell has an engraved, geometric pattern and its feet are underneath the shell with its toes poking out. The turtle’s head is turned to the left and tail turned to the right.
description: The jade sculpture is of a turtle from a bird’s eye view. The turtle is placed so that its head is pointing towards the top-left corner of the image and its tail is pointing towards the bottom-right corner. The turtle’s head is turned to the left. The turtle’s shell has an engraved, geometric pattern and its feet are underneath the shell with its toes poking out. Each of its four feet has three toes. The sculpture is pale green in color with some light yellow wear and brown wear within the engraved details.

alttext: A carved object of a bird in profile faces left clenching a coiled snake in its open hooked beak.
description: The bird’s eye is a carved circle; stylized curly lines give its body texture and definition in the wings and tail feathers. The wing tip that faces the viewer is flat against the bottom. The middle feathers split before the large tail feather swoops toward the right - one curls up and the other curls downward. The snake has an arrow-shaped head with circular eyes and carved scales. Another arrow-headed snake curves under the bird’s tail feather, facing left, centered in the birds open claw. The color is translucent creamy light browns.

alttext: Flat carved pendant of a small bird figure in profile, with carved lines to describe winged details.
description: The bird has a closed hooked beak and wide round eye on its small head as it faces left. Its stylized line-carved wing starts from the left side and swoops up to the top pointing right. Its claw is tucked up along the bottom, as if in flight. There’s a hole on the left side, middle. The color varies from a milky light green to light brown accents, its surface is polished.

caption: front
alttext: A jade ring that is pale brown in color with some darker discoloration. The top part comes to a small point with two different shapes cut out on each side. The bottom comes to a wide, curved point with some engraved lines.
description: The jade ring is pale brown in color with some darker discoloration and shown flat on a dark grey background. The top part comes to a small point with two different shapes cut out on each side. The left side has a short, flat shape that has curled edges on the top and bottom. The right side has a tall, curved shape that reaches up and out. The ring hole is closer to the top part. The bottom comes to a wide, curved point with swirling engraved lines that make a pattern.

alttext: A yellow and orange jade disk with a circle cut out in the middle. There is a pattern of small circles throughout the piece.
description: The yellow and orange jade disk has a circle cut out in the middle and lays flat on a dark grey background. There are caramel and dark brown discolored spots at the top and bottom of the piece. There is a pattern of small circles throughout the piece. The center has a raised lip around it that has small, carved lines that make an encircling pattern.

alttext: A jade sculpture of an oblong cicada. The top is curved with carved lines to detail the head. The middle and bottom are shaped into two longer points with three gold shapes on them. It is light grey in color with brown coloration in the engraved parts.
description: A jade sculpture of an oblong cicada. The image is shown with the sculpture lying flat and head pointing upward. The top is curved with carved lines to detail the head and antennas. The middle and bottom are shaped into two longer points with three gold shapes on them, two closer to the top and one near the bottom-right. It is light grey in color with brown coloration in the engraved parts and in the space between the wings at the center.

alttext: Dragon inspired flat ornament; its head is on the right as it’s turned back to look to the left.
description: The dragon figure is designed in a wave-like shape. A small bird head emerges from the tail on the left with two round eyes, and a small closed hooked beak, with a curl on top of its head. The object has small curled bumps over most of its body that form texture. It’s a creamy light green color with light to brown accents along some of the tips, and its surface is polished. There are two holes next to each other in the top middle.

alttext: A seated woman in traditional dress
description: At center a young woman sits facing the viewer, folding her hands in her lap and smiling with her eyes cast downward. She wears traditional Italian peasant dress with a white top with flowing sleeves, brightly colored embroidered bodice, and a bright blue skirt. She wears a red necklace and earrings and a white head scarf. Lavender and bright red drapery cover the surface on which she sits. Behind her we see an ornately carved wall at left and the base of a stone column at right.

caption: detail of upper left seals (following inscription)
detail of artist signature and seals
detail of artist's inscription, signature and seal
detail of artist signature and seal
detail of inscription, signature and seals

alttext: A road leads from the right to left with a frozen pond on the left and houses on the right.
description: People skate on a frozen pond, one person leans over from a rowboat, and a man and woman pause near the center with a dog nearby, their backs to the viewer. The man has hunched shoulders with long coat, hat, and a walking stick; the woman wears a long dress with winter cape covering her head. A wooden walking bridge extends over a canal, connecting to the road with steps. A few bare trees are rendered between houses. Everything is covered with a light layer of snow. The sky is cloudy overcast and gives the feeling of snow approaching.

alttext: A full moon rises on the left through deep dark blue clouds, over a moody twilight water landscape.
description: The dramatic sky takes up two-thirds of the painting. The estuary water and landscape are textured and flat from the left to center, and rises into hills on the right, there’s a distant slighter hill on the far left. The sublime illumination comes primarily from the moon through moving clouds. A man and woman walk away from the scene on the lower right, near a silhouetted bare tree, a child with them restrains a dog on a leash who’s pointing toward the center. A church and small village rest on the horizon in the gloaming distance.

alttext: A horizontal view of a humble thatched roof cottage, rolling hills and billowing clouds surround three men in the center.
description: A woman in shadow is bent over a washtub near the entrance to cottage on the left, a wide board decrepit fence behind her. The men are having a conversation facing eachother, wearing hats, one has a walking stick. Two more thatched roof cottages with chimneys are seen behind the hills near the center, populated by a few young trees, and a man walking across towards the left, in the distance. There’s a tall spire on the far right behind a grove of trees.

alttext: A two-handled bowl seen from below which is decorated with two large eyes.
description: A red bowl decorated with two large white eyes, with black used to indicate the eyebrows, nose and the iris of the eye.  There is also a teardrop shape on the forehead between the eyebrows.  On either side of the eyes are black nude figures with their arms and legs bent as if they are dancing.  Past those nude figures there are two looped handles which are also painted black.  The bowl has a fluted stem and a flat base, and the stem is hollow, opening up a round hole in the base.

caption: detail of artist signature and seal
Still image from No More, America, a film by Peter Galison, 2017.

alttext: Two fair-skinned ballet dancers in tutus enter on stage from the right.
description: The dancers are dramatically lit from underneath by stage lighting. The dancer in front wears a garland of red flowers around the waist and in hair, her arm is straight out form her waist while her right arm is bent with hand to neck. The dancer behind her poses on one pointed toe and holds a small bouquet of red flowers in her right hand with arms upraised. There’s the suggestion of a third dancer’s elbow and a man in top hat behind her on the right. The background is loose marks of golds and green.

alttext: A Japanese woman in kimono runs across an outdoor platform holding an umbrella against heavy rain.
description: The young woman runs toward the right, bent down with her head under the umbrella, held with both hands, her kimono sleeves flying behind her creating a swooping movement. The kimono, tied in the back, flows around her running legs. Her face is fair and delicate, her black hair is combed back and tied up into a bun. The rain is depicted with heavy diagonal strokes of black ink pouring from a dark cloud in the upper right, with two angular lightning bolts flashing from the sky.

alttext: A young Japanese woman in a kimono stands near a railing of an outdoor platform above water in spring season.
description: The woman wears a decorative kimono of many layers flowing to the floor splayed out but covering her feet. She arches her back slightly, leaning right, her head and neck turned to the right. Her other hand is out of the kimono and holding a long, bended piece of paper with writing on it. Part of an old tree trunk is suggested on the right, with white blooming flowers above. Clusters of yellow water irises emerge from the water, their leaves arching open, as if repeating the woman’s pose. A building exterior is on left, Japanese text written across top.

alttext: A wide brimmed hat rests on right with leafy plants on and alongside it, with calligraphy across the lower half.
description: The shape of the light-colored hat is defined with light hatch marks all around. Plant greens, fresh cut stems, and ribbon wrap around the hat. It’s all displayed horizontally at the top half of the print. The greens appear realistic in color, texture, showing both the front and underside of the leaves. The print has minimal colors of greens, muted orange, browns. Vertical calligraphy lines are written in the bottom half, with a small red seal in middle of the left edge. No background, only the paper’s neutral color.

caption: detail of artist signature and seals

alttext: An old man tumbles upside down through the top of a doorway, while a young man looks at him in surprise.
description: A smiling old man is tumbling upside down through a doorway toward us. The bottom of the door is a closed panel, and the top of the door is open to the outside. To the old man’s right is a young man who is moving away in surprise. The old man’s head, upside down, is at the bottom of the opening in the door. He is bent at the waist, and his feet, with the soles of his shoes facing us, are above his head, as he flips through the door with his hands clenched. The young man’s face is in profile to the left, with his mouth open as he sees the old man. His body is twisted so that his torso swivels to the left as his legs move to the right. He is wearing a vest with black-and-white polka dots.

alttext: A tall Japanese man in kimono robes stands in the center, neck turned and looking to the left.
description: He wears a thin beard and frown, with eyelids painted pink from the corners to above the ears. His grid-patterned robe of green and white is tied and asymmetrically tucked around his waist, black collar. He also wears slim grey, vertical striped pants, with black socks and flat sandals. His arms are nearly hidden in the robes except for one hand peeking out touching his shoulder. A tree branch above frames his head, blooming with pink flowers, perhaps cherry blossoms. The background is warm, muted tones, with simple line drawing of undefined space and a vertical folding shade on right.

alttext: A hanging tapestry featuring a large rock formation at the center with flowers and plants surrounding it. It has a dark blue background and an off-white frame.
description: A rectangular hanging tapestry mounted on a scroll featuring a large rock formation at the center. The formation is off-white and tan colored with many lines throughout it. On top of the formation are thin, green leaves coming out. At the bottom-right of the formation are many white flowers with long, green leaves bent at an angle. Below them are more small formations that are colored blue and off-white. It has a dark blue background and an off-white frame.

Prince Shōtoku at Age Two, Japanese, Kamakura period, datable to c. 1292. Wood (hinoki cypress) with polychromy; inlaid rock crystal (quartz) eyes. Harvard Art Museums/Arthur M. alttext: A wooden sculpture of a young boy standing upright. The boy is wearing a long, red piece of clothing that goes from his hips and covers his feet. His hands are together in front of his chest. The boy is bald and is looking down at his hands.
description: The wooden sculpture is of a young boy standing upright and facing the viewer. He is wearing a red piece of clothing that goes from his hips and covers his feet. His hands are together and in front of his chest. His face is very round with round red lips, slender eyes that gaze down at his hands, and furrowed brows. He is bald and is colored black on the top part of his body and golden colored on the bottom part.
