alttext: A landscape showing openings to caves in the side of a cliff wall
description: At lower left, a large rock with green leafy plants growing on it emerges in the extreme foreground. Beyond it, in the middle distance, are large boulders and rocky terrain dotted with trees and vegetation, in which two deer are grazing at lower right. Beyond the rocks, dominating the upper half of the piece, large, light brown cliff walls rise up, surmounted by grass and trees under bright blue sky. At center right is a dark, arch-shaped opening in the rocky cliff wall. Further up at extreme right is another, larger cave opening.

caption: detail of artist's signature and seal

alttext: A curved pale teal bowl with a bare foot.
description: A curved pale teal colored bowl shown on a white background from the side. It has curved walls and a small, bare foot. The lip is faded from thinned glaze.

alttext: Twenty-three girls and a nun sit in four rows in this group photograph. Their faces peer at the viewer.
description: The girls all wear white bonnets and blouses of different patterns and long skirts. Many of them have their hands folded in their laps. A young nun sits on the right. Four small girls sit in the front row. No one is smiling, probably to sit still for the long exposure. Behind the group is drapery strewn over a board or wall. The image is delicate and low contrast overall, with a small amount of light blue haze occurring in some white areas and the background.

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped gold coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: On the side of the coin on the left is the head of a woman facing left, wearing a necklace, her hair is tied back with tendrils hanging down. Small dots surround the border along with the Greek characters: K A. The other side of the coin depicts a kneeling man facing right wrestling a lion. The man’s right arm wrapped around the lion’s head, its paws bracing itself on man’s knee.

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped gold coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: On the side of the coin on the left is the bust of a man facing left, clean shaven with short tendrils of curly hair held in place with a laurel wreath, loose clothing draped over shoulders; surrounding the border, small dots and the Latin characters: I M P / C A E S / D I V I / V E S P / F / D O M I T I A N / A V G. The other side of the coin depicts a woman seated on a highly decorated hexagonal shield facing right, bare chested and draped from the waist down, knees bent with left arm raised placing  head in hand in a show of mourning: below, a broken spear; surrounding the border, small dots and the Latin characters: G E R M A N I C V S / C O S / X.

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped bronze gold colored coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: Within the circle on the left is the profile of a naked man facing right, kneeling on one knee. In his left hand is a bow. His right arm is bent and raised above his head holding a club. Behind on the left is a large fish facing up. The circle on the right depicts four imprinted squares, side by side and one on top of the other.

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped silver-gray coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: On the side of the coin on the left is a barely visible man on a four-horse drawn vehicle facing left, wearing flowing clothing, a stick in his right hand, and the reins of the horses in his left. Above flies a barely visible winged woman holding a wreath to crown the man. Below, a line under the horses is an assortment of armor. The other side of the coin depicts the head of a woman facing left, wearing a necklace, dangling earing, her hair is tied back in a headband. Four dolphins surround her head along the border. Below, the Greek characters: E Y A I N E.

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped silver-gray coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: On the side of the coin on the left is a woman seated in a tree on a throne facing right, head slightly turned, naked from the waist up, right hand raised, with tree limbs and foliage radiating out from behind; to the left of the throne, the Greek characters: A P I. The other side of the coin depicts a bull standing facing right, head turned facing back; above, barely legible Greek characters.

alttext: A black and white photograph of a landscape portrays four man the margins of a lake.
description: A black and white photograph of a landscape portrays four man in the margins of a lake. The lake  is located on the left side of the picture. On the right, close to the water, big rocks are scattered around the edge. Two man are sitting on the rocks and the other two are standing. A small hill filled with trees is found on the right and background of the picture.

caption: after treatment
alttext: A long, rectangular textile fragment with a red ground and animal figures woven in yellow with black, green, blue, and pink details.
description: The tapestry-woven woolen textile is rectangular, with the central band largely intact. Two narrow stripes that border the top and bottom are largely missing with only the warp structure is present. The remaining weft depicts a multicolored geometric pattern. The central band has a red ground decorated with various animal figures worked mostly in yellow, with black, blue and green details. Small yellow roundels across the top, bottom, and middle of the red stripe are connected with a vine pattern to create diamonds that frame the figures.

caption: after treatment
alttext: A rectangular textile fragment showing two vertical bands in black depicting lions, rabbits, riders, dancers/hunters, birds, and flowers on a yellowed, off-white ground.
description: The rectangular tunic fragment has two vertical bands of design worked in black on an undyed, heavily yellowed ground fabric. The pattern depicts lions, rabbits, riders, dancers/hunters, birds, and flowers bordered by stripes with a small wave pattern and blocks of color at the bottom edge imitating a fringe.

alttext: A round textile fragment in purple and off-white showing densely packed dancers, putti, lions, flowers, fish, birds, and other animals with a solid purple border and smaller purple circle with an off-white twist.
description: The circular textile fragment is tapestry-woven in purple and off-white. The outer border is solid purple surrounding a densely packed motif of dancers, putti, lions, flowers, fish, birds, and other animals. In the middle of the motif is another smaller purple circle with an off-white twist pattern.

caption:
upper row, left to right: 1977.216.1795.1, 2 and 3
lower row, l to r: .4 and 5

Maruyama Ōkyo, Peacock and Peonies, Japanese, Edo period, 1768. Hanging scroll; ink, color, and gold on silk. Promised gift of Robert S. and Betsy G. Feinberg, TL42147.17. Photo: John Tsantes and Neil Greentree; © Robert Feinberg.

alttext: A rectangular carpet with a thick orange border that has a dark green, red, and white geometric floral pattern. At the center is a smaller rectangle space that has a large red shape that is rectangle at the bottom and comes to a diamond shape at the top. It is detailed with a white border and above it is a simple geometric floral motif in green and red with a white background.
description: The rectangular carpet lies flat vertically and has a thick orange border that has a dark green, red, and white geometric floral pattern. There is a smaller detailed white border outside of the larger border and a yellow inside border. At the center is a smaller rectangle space that has a large red shape that is rectangle at the bottom and comes to a diamond shape at the top. The shape has a circular detail at its bottom center, a smaller circular detail at its top, and is detailed with a small white border. Above the shape is a simple geometric floral motif in green and red with a white background.

caption: recto
alttext: A seated nude woman facing away and holding a towel
description: Softly textured gray lines depict a seated nude woman facing away from the viewer and leaning forward and turned to the right. With her right hand she holds a towel up to the side of her head, obscuring her face. Her left hand holds the edge of the cushion on which she sits. Her hair is accented with brown chalk and touches of blue and olive indicate the background at her left. Dark shading at lower right sets off her pale front right leg bent in front of her.

caption: detail of central medallion with Venus and Adonis

alttext: A loosely sketched drawing of a group of figures, some wearing robes and head coverings.
description: A loosely sketched drawing of two groups of figures. The six figures in the group on the right are wearing robes and head coverings. Some are carrying objects under their arms. They face left and towards the three figures in the group on the left. The three figures on the left have no head coverings and wear traditional clothes. The lead figure from the group on the right is handing an object to a figure from the left group.

alttext: Long rectangular buckle, slightly bowed, featuring two dragon-like animals in relief slinking across the object, eyes locked on each other.
description: The larger dragon figure faces left, as its curly stylized body slinks along the surface. It has two flattened ears, carved eyebrows, wide nose, and deep set-eyes that look down at a smaller cat-like animal, with an arched back, whose head is close to the ground but turned to look up at the dragon. We see the top of its head and ears as it enters in from the left. Both have curling tails and shadows underneath their bodies. A flat bracket-shaped opening is seen underneath at the bottom. Bone colored and pale green variations, polished surface.

caption: detail of marks in one of four corners

alttext: A black and white print in two panels with text on the right panel.
description: The print show two black panels bordered in white. A cluster of stars in the lower right of the left panel fan out and grow less dense across both panels. The right panel shows a page from a Bengali language newspaper published in Kolkata, from of January 1, 2014. Areas of the page are black squares and rectangles, the right side shows a large black vertical rectangle, the bottom of the page is a large black horizontal rectangle.

alttext: A black and white print in two panels with text on the right panel.
description: The print show two black panels bordered in white. A widely spaced pattern of stars covers the black surface of both panels. The right panel shows a page from the British newspaper, The Guardian, of January 1, 2014. Immediately beneath the masthead is a black rectangle followed by a black square. The bottom half shows text with two. A rectangle and a square have been placed over the text of the bottom portion of the page.

alttext: A black and white print in two panels with text on the right panel.
description: A print of seven black squares and rectangles with white speckles, with a page of text from the Mexican newspaper “Reforma” from which squares have been removed. A large, black, vertical rectangle makes up the left half. A horizontal black rectangle at the top of the right half, a white border separates it from the newspaper, three rectangles are on the left of the newspaper. There is a  headline in large type, with text below, and a small black rectangle; beneath the text is a larger black rectangle, a second headline with text following and a smaller black rectangle.

alttext: A black and white print in two panels with text on the right panel.
description: The print show two black panels bordered in white. A widely spaced pattern of stars covers the black surface of both panels. The right panel shows a page from The New York Times newspaper for January 1, 2014, portions of the text have been replaced with square and rectangles of black with a widely spaced pattern of black dots. The name has been partially obscured by a mailing label.

alttext: A black and white print in two panels with text on the right panel.
description: The print show two black panels bordered in white. A widely spaced pattern of stars covers the black surface of both panels. The right panel is divided into four horizontally. The top is a narrow black rectangle followed by a white strip, a banner from The Sydney Morning Herald for Wednesday, January 1, 2014. A black square is next followed by a white strip of text. A black rectangle is below that, another line of text borders the panel.

alttext: Fair-skinned young woman (Venus) rides in a floral covered chariot with a cherub and two doves near the front.
description: Venus sits back in the delicate chariot facing toward left while looking into a small gold mirror. She’s partially nude with a gold decorative belt around her waist and white drapery painted with small gold stars covering her lap. Some of her hair is up in a small bun, the rest flows down across her left shoulder. The figures are white from the porcelain with delicate hand painted facial features. The cherub holds loosely to a pink ribbon leading to the two doves in front. The flowing flowers are painted in pastel colors, the wheels are trimmed in gold paint.

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped gold coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: On the side of the coin on the left is the bust of a man facing front, with a large cross behind him, wearing a beard, draped in loose fitting clothing, right hand raised with index and middle finger raised, left hand holding a book with rectangular raised dots on the cover; surrounding the border, the characters: D N / I h S / C n S / R E X / R E G N A N T I U M. The other side of the coin depicts the bust of a man facing front, wearing a beard with a crown on top of head, wrapped in clothing with a diamond pattern with a dots in the middle, right hand raised holding a cross, left hand holding an orb with the letters P A X on it, with a small cross on top; surrounding the border, the characters: [I V S] T I N I A N V S / M V L T V S.

caption: Sim Chi Yin (Singaporean, b. 1978), Mountain range surrounding the Nevada Test Site, November 2017. Archival pigment print. From the series Most People Were Silent. Harvard Art Museums/Fogg Museum, Richard and Ronay Menschel Fund for the Acquisition of Photographs, 2020.181. Artwork: © Sim Chi Yin; image courtesy of the artist.

alttext: A large round green-gray jar decorated with dark flowing lines in a floral pattern
description: From its flat circular base, the jar widens gradually up until the top third. There, it quickly curves back inward toward the center where a wide opening is ringed by a ridged cuff. With subtle horizontal striations across its surface, it is glazed in a muted green-gray, with decorative lines in dark olive. The top third shows a border featuring curving a geometric design. In a broad band across most of the side, a floral design of leaves and stems in flowing lines is set off by dark spaces, and a more narrow border at the bottom features a repeating leaf shape.

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped gold coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: On the side of the coin on the left is the bust of a man facing slightly right, wearing chest armor and crested helmet with a pearl headband, right arm raised behind him holding a spear, a shield on left arm. Surrounding the border, the Latin characters: F L / I V L / C O N S T A N T I V S / P E R P / A V G. The other side of the coin depicts two women sitting on thrones facing each other, the one on the right holding a staff with foot on a stand, both holding an inscribed shield between them. Surrounding the borders, the Latin characters: G L O R I A / R E I P V B L I C A E / V O T / X X X  / M V L T / X X X X.

alttext: A page of a book with text in French and an illustration of a woman looking in a mirror
description: An illustration and a block of text are both printed in olive green on cream colored paper. The text is indented to the right, except at the bottom third, where the lines of text begin closer to the left. In the space at upper left is a light sketch of a woman in an evening gown. Seen from behind, she stands looking at her reflection in a full length mirror as she appears to come her hair back. In a lower corner we see the reflection of a man in a tuxedo who apparently stands behind her, looking on.

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped silver-gray coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: On the side of the coin on the left is the bust of a bearded man facing right, short tendrils of curly hair held in place with a laurel wreath, loose clothing draped over shoulders; surrounding the border, small dots and the Latin characters: I M P / C / M / O P E L / S E V / M A C R I N V S / A V G. The other side of the coin depicts a woman standing facing left, draped in loose fitting clothing, right arm extended holding a vertical staff, left arm resting on a small column; surrounding the border, small dots and the Latin characters: P O N T I F / M A X / T R / P / C O S / P P.

alttext: Brightly colored circular dish with scene of tree, city, figures, and man with deer head
description: In the foreground of this painted dish is a man in a short blue robe facing away from the viewer. Rather than a human head, he has a long snout and low ears. Facing his feet are a pair of orange dogs. To the left is a rectangular pool of water full of several nude figures. They face the deer-headed man. In the background is a very tall tree, a large river, a boulder, and a city that stretches all the way to the horizon. The pigments in this painting are vibrant, including bright orange, lush green, and deep blue.

alttext: Still life of pink and white roses fill a decorative Chinese vase.
description: A vase is placed right of center as the garden roses and leaves hang over the vase, filling the empty space on the left. Seven full roses are seen in various angles and stages of bloom from opening bud to an aging bloom. The large cylindrical vase is detailed with warriors galloping on white horses and swords out, against a brown background. The vase sits on a shiny wooden table, its reflection is seen in the varnish, as well as the wood grain. The background behind the vase is undescribed hues of blues and greens.

caption: detail of duty mark on underside of largest jar (.1)

alttext: A group of figures in formal wear conversing by the entrance to a corridor
description: At left a small group of men in top hats and dark suits stand conversing with two women in white tutus. At center left,  one man stands in three quarter profile facing away from us, folding his hand behind his back and looking on as the women talk. Another man stands behind him also looking on, and at extreme left two other men stand facing away from us and partially blocking view of the two dancers.  Extending out of view at right we see a dimly lit hallway with two brightly lit open doorways.

alttext: Front and back views of an ornate silver medallion depicting two Christian religious scenes.
description: One side shows two nude figures (Adam and Eve) standing beside a tree looking up as Eve reaches for fruit. Animals and people surround the couple along the edge. A snake raises its head in bottom center between them. The other side depicts three men hanging on crosses. The man in center (Christ) has arms outstretched, a Roman solider in lower left holds a spear to his waist. Also on the ground, other soldiers with spears look up to Christ in center. Two women kneel away facing lower left. Both sides are engraved with lettering along outer edges.

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped silver-gray coin with relief decoration on each side.
description:
On the side of the coin on the left is a man riding on a horse facing right, wearing clothing consisting of a grid pattern, holding a whip; surrounding the border, the Greek characters: B A S E L E O S / B A S I L E O N / M E G A R O U / A Z O U. The other side of the coin depicts a woman standing facing right, holding a spear and shield, symbols to the left, right, and above.

.

caption: recto
alttext: A drawing of a nude man picking up a stone.
description: The drawing in graphite on white paper depicts a nude man leaning to the ground to pick up a stone. The man’s stance is wide, his right leg stretched behind him to the left of the page. His torso is stooped over his bent left knee, his right arm curled toward his left shoulder, his left arm outstretched to reach a stone to the bottom right of the page. His face is turned behind him to the left of the page, fixed in a glaring expression. There are a number of suggested renderings of different arm positions drawn outward from the subject’s shoulders. There is a suggestion of a grid drawn over the figure.

alttext: A lion standing on partial platforms.
description: A lion which stretches forward so that its back legs are lengthened and its front legs are bent and kept close to its head, almost invisible.  Its tail curls into a circle, and its back feet stand on a shape which is connected to the backs the paws, suggesting the surface that the lion should be standing on which is currently missing.  Its front paws rest on a wide platform like a step, and are brought together under the lions chin and open mouth.  The step is held up on a perpendicular shape which is triangular with scalloped edges.

alttext: A large group of barefoot figures gathered in a circle outdoors.
description: A group of men are gathered in a tight circle with an even tighter inner group inside, most wearing robes around their waists. Some are bearded though their faces lack detail. Many are slightly bent at the waist and leaning to the right, some are raising up one arm bent at the elbow, others are raising clubs or handmade weapons. Light and shadow give depth to the gray wash drawing. The shadows of all fall towards the right. The background is loosely defined outdoor space of flat ground.

alttext: An image of a piece of paper with writing on it on a brown background.
description: The image is of a long, narrow piece of paper that is centered on a brown background. The background is irregular in color and has a wooden-like pattern. The paper is placed at the top-center and is vertical. There are three vertical rows of writing in black ink on the paper in Chinese. The writing is largest in size at the right of the paper and is smaller in size in the center and left rows. At the bottom-left is a small red square with written symbols in it. Below the paper to the bottom left is a small horizontal label that says “No. 8.” There is a small, brown wear mark at the bottom left of the paper.

caption: recto
alttext: A drawing of a city of low buildings with tile roofs.
A rectangular scroll depicting a tall rock form with a man looking up at it. The scroll has much writing in Chinese at the top.
description: A rectangular off-white scroll depicting a tall rock form to the left with a man looking up at it from the right. The rock is irregularly shaped and has dark, jagged lines that show texture throughout it. The man is wearing a blue robe and has his hands raised together toward the rock. He has a black hat and holds a white rectangular object in his hands. There are small mountains in the background. The scroll has much calligraphy writing in Chinese at the top. There are three red, square Chinese symbols among the writing.

alttext: A circular dish shown from the side. It is pale blue-green with a thin, off-white rim.
description: A circular dish shown from the side on a white background. It is low and wide with the rim curving up. It is pale blue-green with a thin, off-white rim. There are some small cracks in the glaze throughout.

caption: Maida and George Abrams Collection, Boston

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped silver-gray coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: On the side of the coin on the left is a heavily worn celery leaf, consisting of five leaves radiating out from a single stem. The other side of the coin depicts a heavily worn celery leaf inside of a square.

caption: recto
alttext: A drawing of a seated woman spinning thread.
description: The drawing in graphite on white paper depicts a woman seated center-page facing the viewer; her head turned to the right in profile. She wears a plain sleeveless dress gathered at the shoulders with circular brooches. To the right of the page is a spinning mechanism: a tall ornamental column topped with a narrow dowel. She guides thread from a mass of fibers at the top of the dowel with her left hand. The thread crosses her torso into her right hand, where she turns it onto a spool. There is written script at the bottom center of the page.

alttext: Both sides of an irregularly shaped silver-gray coin with relief decoration on each side.
description: On the side of the coin on the left is a turtle as seen from above, with five circles on its shell and two lateral forming a T shaped pattern, flippers jutting out of the four corners of the shell, head and tail from the top and bottom. The other side of the coin depicts two triangle and three irregular rectangles indented in the coin.

alttext: Figure drawing of a man in the clouds above and two figures below within an arch.
description: The man (Christ) is drawn at the top half of the arch, raises his right arm up, palm up, dressed in robes, with a halo around his head suggested by negative space. At the bottom half, a person on the left leans into the middle, lowered head resting on arms. The second man stands on the right, turned and looking right, his right arm raised above the head of the other person, his left arm is at his side, both wearing ancient dress. There’s a distant landscape of hills, water, and arched bridge in the middle.

alttext: A jade hook that is off-white in color on a black background. It is long and narrow and is geometric in shape. There is a small foot that holds up the center part. The left side curls up while the right side slopes down.
description: The jade hook is off-white in color on a black background. It is long and narrow with a small foot that holds up the center part. The entire piece has been cut into clean, straight geometric shapes with three small peaks in the middle part. The left side curls up while the right side slopes down.

alttext: A black and white print portrays a building with a tower on the middle of its roof, several houses surround the tower.
description: A black and white print portrays a one-story building with a tower found on the middle of the print, houses and trees are found on both sides of the structure. On the left a darker area is depicted, and a wooden boat is stationed on the side. A dirt road Is found on the right, a man, a woman, and a child are walking on it.

alttext: A drawing of a cottage depicts two men and two figures working in a yard.
description: A drawing of cottage with a broken roof and two chimneys. A man is standing on the left corner facing the house and another one is in front of the main entrance. A man(?) and a woman are shown working on some fabrics on the ground, a dog is with them.

alttext: A woman in a harlequin costume rides a donkey as a marching band follows
description: Lines sketched in blue on a white background show a scene of a woman in a harlequin costume astride a donkey, leading a marching band. The group of figures are all shown in three quarter profile, facing toward us and turning toward the left. At lower left, the head of the donkey approaches, looking forward and past the viewer. The woman wears a suit with dark pantaloons and a frilly collar and shoulders, and on her head   a feathered headdress. Marching behind and around her, we see uniformed  band members following.

alttext: A black and white photograph of paintings made of stacked sheets of glass.
description: The black and white photograph shows a grid of ten square across and eleven down. Each square in the grid has another grid within it. Some of the squares have mottled surfaces, others show another smaller grid, some are nearly blacked out. The darker squares are fewer in number and are spaced out across the surface.

caption: recto
alttext: A drawing of standing nude female figure and a seated figure with a tambourine.
description: The drawing in graphite on tracing paper depicts two figures rendered in sparse contour under a grid. On the upper left of the page is a figures arm reaching up, visible only from the elbow. To the right and beneath the arm in a seated figure in a sleeved robe and tall hat holding a tambourine. On the right of the page is a nude female figure standing on her toes and twisting her arms above her head in a suggestion of dance.

alttext: Two female figures inside a paintings gallery. One stands with her back towards us, holding a cane. The other is sitting, reading a book and facing the viewer.
description: An image of the inside a paintings gallery from the perspective of an open doorway. The figure closest to the viewer is sitting on a bench, wearing an elegant ballgown, and reading a book. Her face has no detail or discerning characteristics. Her long dress is pleated, and she wears a black hat and a single black buckled shoe is visible. Directly behind her is a standing woman, with her right arm outstretched leaning back on her cane. She appears to wear a black hat with feather adornments, and an elegant long-sleeved ballgown with ruffles on the sleeve. Her back is towards the viewer, with suggestions of two framed paintings on the wall in the background.
